An '''iron rock''' is a protruding rock containing [[iron ore]]. A player with a [[Mining]] level of 15 or higher can mine iron ore from rocks found in various [[mines]], granting 35 Mining [[experience]] for each ore mined. After being mined, an iron rock takes 5.4 seconds to [[respawn]].

Iron is the most popular ore that [[free-to-play]] players [[Power levelling|power-mine]] for experience. At the [[Mining Guild]], [[Al Kharid Mine]], [[Piscatoris Mine]], [[Legends' Guild mine]], [[Verdant Valley]], [[Lovakengj Mine]], [[Mount Karuulm Mine]], [[Trahaearn Mine]], [[Wilderness Resource Area]], and [[Isle of Souls mine]], there are three rocks in a triangle formation, which allows for convenient mining.

